    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"816344\">Aaron Liu</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113488-general/topic/Adding.20an.20AddCommMonoid.20instance.20breaks.20rw.20tactic/near/520141269\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>That example doesn't work for me. What version of mathlib are you on?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>\"4.17.0-rc1\" apparently</p>",
